title: [Tukero's Magic Shoppe]
[Tukero's Outfitting]
description: Enclosed by smooth sandstone walls, the shop features an ivory elven noble statue in the center of its hardwood floor.  A fringed crimson silk banner hangs under the haon ceiling.  Right near the front is a large oak table.
